claim: A mixtape is a home-made compilation of music.
premise_source_doc_sentence: A mixtape  (  also mix-tape or mix tape  )  is a home-made compilation of music  (  typically copyrighted songs taken from other sources  )  recorded in a specific order , traditionally onto a cassette tape , though later replaced by CD or MP3 playlist formats .
